Summary of Changes:
State Management:
Added selectedAnswers state to keep track of user selections.
Handling Answer Changes:
Added a function handleAnswerChange to update the selectedAnswers state when a user selects an answer.
Fetching Quiz Data:
Added error handling.
Processed and combined answers directly within the question objects.
Used Promise.all to ensure all questions and their answers are resolved before setting the state.
Dynamic Rendering:
Used map to iterate over questions and answers, dynamically generating the question text and answer options.
Ensured each question's answers are grouped and uniquely identified.
Managed the checked state of radio buttons based on user selections.
Enhanced layout and styling for better user experience.